  "text": "The assumptions used in this study include: the plasma jet flow is time-dependent during the computation, axisymetric and turbulent, the plasma is in the LTE and the radiation heat loss is neglected, all the plasma properties are temperature dependent, the swirling velocity component in the plasma jet can be neglected in comparison with the axial velocity, the plasma jet flow is incompressible [CITATION_1] , then obeys to the condition low Mach number, hence the compression work and the viscous dissipation can be neglected in the energy equation and finally the gravity effect is neglected.",
